text: Nice church for wedding ceremony, with great pastor and nice light coming through the glass during the day. Atmosphere is excellent. (photos copyright: team of @kai_picture )

I'm really glad to visit this place for the first time. I joined Reformed Evangelical Church Singapore (GRII Singapore) for the first time and glad to hear the sermon from Pastor Stephen Tong, which is I always heard him preaching at Reformed Evangelical Church Indonesia in Jakarta (Kemayoran). What a peaceful church and the exit way was connected to Queenstown MRT station.
True Way Presbyterian Church never fail to attract my attention when the train stops at Queenstown MRT station. It look very peacefulÂ ...
Came here for a guitar jam. It's an interesting concept if you just want to take your guitar and play medley after medley and challenge your guitar chord change skills.
Great community church with services in English, Chinese and Indonesian. Very conveniently located by Queenstown MRT station.
